
NOTE:

Please use the provided Installer Script.
It will NOT scatter files all over your system.
Everything is still put in your Crazy 8's directory.

Your existing scores will NOT be erased.

Nothing you have added to your Crazy 8's drawer
will be erased.

There are some new features added to this version, but 
not all of the Guides were updated to explain them.

If you have any problems, please read the English Guide.

Sorry for any inconvienience.



